12 Senate Bill Proposes Expanding VA Telehealth Services Across State Lines 
Healthcare Informatics: A bill introduced in the U.S. Senate aims to improve healthcare access for veterans by expanding Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) telehealth services across state lines.
